==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Intemperately
<hw>In*tem`per*ate*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In an
intemperate manner; immoderately; excessively; without
restraint.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The people . . . who behaved very unwisely and
<qex>intemperately</qex> on that occasion.</q>
<rj><qau>Burke.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Intemperateness</ent>⟦br⟧
